last_name: Van Der Bilt MD, PhD, FESC, FEACVI
sub_title: Cardiologist Haga Teaching Hospital, The Hague. Assistant professor in Cardiology University Medical Center Utrecht
summary:
Senior Cardiologist in Haga Teaching Hospital The Hague
Head of department of Echocardiography
Head of interventional MRI Ablation Center 
Assistant Professor in Cardiology UMC Utrecht

Special interest in non-invasive cardiac imaging with emphasis on echocardiography and cardiac MRI.
Special interest in e-health and use of AI in medicine
Special interest in online education
Member of MCQ writing group ESC European Exam in General Cardiology
Dutch representative cardiac section UEMS

Holder of current EACVI Transthoracic and Transesophageal echocardiography certificates

Cardiac CT level 2 trained
